### What this diagram deliberately does *not* show

- **Conditional branches or failure paths** — Domain Storytelling is
  happy-path only. Failures live in T3.2 fallback decision trees or in
  the canvas § Open Questions.
- **Aggregate or BC structure** — see Aggregate Conceptual Model
  (`03-aggregate-conceptual-model.md`) for the static model.
- **Time spans / SLAs** — the numbered steps are sequential, not
  durations.
- **Other stories in the same domain** — each story gets its own T4.3
  file (`<NN>-domain-stories-<story-slug>.md`).

