## Legend

| Glyph / shape | Domain Storytelling concept | Mermaid approximation |
|---------------|------------------------------|------------------------|
| 👤 yellow rounded | Actor (Person, Group, IT-System) | classDef `actor` |
| 📄 blue rectangle | Work Object (document, record, artifact) | classDef `workObject` |
| ⚙ purple diamond | Activity (verb-phrase, work being done) | classDef `activity` |
| Numbered edge | Chronological step in the story | `-->|"N. label"|` |

The canonical Hofer/Schwentner notation uses illustrated icons for these
roles (a stick figure, a folded document, a gear). Mermaid does not
render those — the colour-coded classes above are this skill's
honest approximation.

